    • Strided convoluti= ons *CORRECTION*

    At 4:44 when Andrew= was explaining the technical note on cross-correlation vs convolution, the= flipping of the filter was incorrect.

    Originally, it was:

    34510= 2-197

    <= p>The correct filter after flipping vertically and horizontally would be:
    79-1
    20= 1
    543
    =

    What Andrew did was more a flip over the diagonal.
